.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ACojoaXtxS8yGNyCm_l4F0kdPAw=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JLKJL5WKXDWRBRW6IAHDTUYXRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FACojoaXtxS8yGNyCm_l4F0kdPAw%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJLKJL5WKXDWRBRW6IAHDTUYXRM.jpg&h=3818b692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n栗戰書女兒栗潛心<br />\n<br />\n至於栗潛心的伴侶蔡華波，則不似大掩飾自己的財富，2017年以太和控股的名義，收購半島酒店的大量股份及..................................<br />\n<br />\n《紐時》分析，「港版國安法」一為中共在香港壓制異見「提供了一個強大的新武器」，可以保......................................<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"993eacf7412cb8f1747039eb42e6c4d2b4988b80","tid":2154449,"uid":313615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\"><strong>才5000萬美元，在偉大的習總書記領導下中國人均生產總值已突破八千萬美元，建議將栗公公納入低保</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b05840cb72c7bfd1fa72bee1381c1d016e3f33ca","tid":2154449,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"(紐約時報)太子黨在港擁值51M USD豪宅物業<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fNBaeS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fNBaeS</a>"},{"pid":"8ab79069dbc2a79a8728ea2818efbb33acc2b9d9","tid":2154449,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}